lo\n|\n|-\n| 2020\n| Hunter Hunter\n| Mersault\n|\n|}\n\n=== Television ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! class=\"unsortable\" | Notes\n|-\n|1989\n|''[[Unsub (TV series)|Unsub]]''\n|Young John Wesley\n|Episode: \"And the Dead Shall Rise to Condemn Thee: Part 2\"\n|-\n|1992\u20131994\n| data-sort-value=\"Odyssey, The\" |''[[The Odyssey (TV series)|The Odyssey]]''\n|Yudo\n|Episodes: \"The Believers\", \"The Hall of Darkness\", \"The Prophecy\"\n|-\n|1993\n|''[[1994 Baker Street: Sherlock Holmes Returns|Sherlock Holmes Returns]]''\n|Young Booth\n|TV film\n|-\n|1995\n|''[[Lonesome Dove|Lonesome Dove: The Outlaw Years]]''\n|Hank Valen\n|Episode: \"The Hanging\"\n|-\n|1995\u20131996\n|''[[Action Man (1995 TV series)|Action Man]]''\n|Additional Voices\n|26 episodes\n|-\n|1996\n|''[[Night of the Twisters]]''\n|Dan Hatch\n|TV film\n|-\n|1996\n|''[[Robin of Locksley (film)|Robin of Locksley]]''\n|Robin McAllister\n|TV film\n|-\n|2003\n|''[[Spider-Man: The New Animated Series]]''\n|[[Flash Thompson]] (voice)\n|Episode: \"Flash Memory\"\n|-\n|2010\n|''[[NCIS: Los Angeles]]''\n|Matt Bernhart\n|Episode: \"The Bank Job\"\n|-\n|2010\u20132013\n|''[[Nikita (TV series)|Nikita]]''\n|Owen Elliot / Sam Matthews\n| Recurring (seasons 1\u20132); main role (seasons 3\u20134)\n|-\n|2015\n|''Broad Squad''\n|Patrick Byrne\n|TV film\n|-\n|2016\n|''Real Detective''\n|Detective Eddie Herman\n|Episode: \"Redemption\"\n|-\n|2017\n| ''[[Somewhere Between (TV series)|Somewhere Between]]''\n| Nico Jackson\n| Main role\n|-\n|2018\n|''[[Hawaii Five-0 (2010 TV series)|Hawaii Five-0]]''\n|Brad Woodward\n|Episode: \"O Ka Mea Ua Hala, Ua Hala Ia\"/\"What Is Gone Is Gone\"\n|}\n\n==Awards==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Award\n! Category\n! Work\n! Result\n|- \n| 1997\n|[[18th Youth in Film Awards|Young Artist Awards]]\n| Best Performance in a TV Movie / Mini-Series \u2013 Young Actor\n|''[[Night of the Twisters (film)|Night of the Twisters]]''\n| {{Nom}}